data.actual_result: It doesn't transfer over, and it stays empty.
data.expected_result: Your search content should transfer over, like "Add Friend" option.
data.short_description: "Join a server" button doesn't translate the content you have typed into the "join server" screen.
data.steps_to_repro: - Go to quickswitcher, and type some gibberish stuffs in there that will give no results. - First, hit the "Add Friend" button. See how your gibberish content transfers over. - Then, hit the back button, and press on "Join a server". - Observe how your content doesn't transfer over.
